{"id": 57650, "date": "2025-07-08T04:00:26", "date_gmt": "2025-07-08T11:00:26", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=57650"}, "modified": "2026-03-02T15:15:26", "modified_gmt": "2026-03-02T23:15:26", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-july-8-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/08/kingdom-of-days-july-8-2/", "title": {"rendered": "July 8"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1973:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band headline two shows at The Main Point in Bryn Mawr, Pennsylvania.</p>\n<p><strong>1975:\u00a0</strong>Bruce completes &#8220;Linda Let Me Be The One&#8221; at the Record Plant in New York City. It will remain in the vault for 23 years.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/G4yx0JdiKfo?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=RDG4yx0JdiKfo\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1977:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band work on &#8220;The Promise&#8221; and &#8220;Talk to Me&#8221; during recording sessions at Atlantic Studios in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>One day after their legendary Roxy show, Bruce and the boys take the Darkness Tour to the Arizona Veterans Memorial Coliseum in Phoenix, where several songs are filmed and released as promotional clips (and later included in the <em>Darkness on the Edge of Town </em>30th anniversary box set). Bruce&#8217;s official video for &#8220;Rosalita (Come Out Tonight)&#8221; is from this show. &#8220;Raise Your Hand&#8221; is filmed but not released, but you can watch it below.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/YAxyHv7k0hA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/CYHGh6lmSbo?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/BNwpbW0wCAI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/okrvOAUg-yY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/lpjqgGNUcG4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/qWChNHrQ-SQ?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"19451\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1978-07-08/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1978-07-08.jpg?fit=1254%2C904&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1254,904\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1593061312&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1978-07-08\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1978-07-08.jpg?fit=300%2C216&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1978-07-08.jpg?fit=758%2C546&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19451 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1978-07-08.jpg?resize=758%2C546&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"546\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1978-07-08.jpg?w=1254&amp;ssl=1 1254w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1978-07-08.jpg?resize=300%2C216&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1978-07-08.jpg?resize=1024%2C738&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1978-07-08.jpg?resize=768%2C554&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1981:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play their fifth of six nights at the Brendan Byrne Arena in East Rutherford, as the River Tour continues. Two songs&#8211;&#8220;Two Hearts&#8221; and &#8220;Candy&#8217;s Room&#8221;&#8211;will be released on <em>Live 1975-85</em>. Before the show, Bruce soundchecks his original song &#8220;All I Need,&#8221; which he would eventually donate to Gary U.S. Bonds for his\u00a0<em>On the Line</em> album.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Q6CRuzDAzkM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=RDQ6CRuzDAzkM\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/9zr4sVzdVtc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/IceVgtyvGY8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>The Born in the U.S.A. Tour treks across Ohio for the first of two nights in Richfield.</p>\n<div id=\"v-CKvko768-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/CKvko768?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"19452\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1984-07-09a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-09a.jpg?fit=1251%2C799&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1251,799\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1593061770&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1984-07-09a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-09a.jpg?fit=300%2C192&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-09a.jpg?fit=758%2C484&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19452 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-09a.jpg?resize=758%2C484&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"484\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-09a.jpg?w=1251&amp;ssl=1 1251w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-09a.jpg?resize=300%2C192&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-09a.jpg?resize=1024%2C654&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-09a.jpg?resize=768%2C491&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"19453\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1984-07-09b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-09b.jpg?fit=863%2C958&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"863,958\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1593061796&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1984-07-09b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-09b.jpg?fit=270%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-09b.jpg?fit=758%2C841&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19453 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-09b.jpg?resize=758%2C841&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"841\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-09b.jpg?w=863&amp;ssl=1 863w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-09b.jpg?resize=270%2C300&amp;ssl=1 270w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-09b.jpg?resize=768%2C853&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1985:\u00a0</strong>Barely a year after its release,\u00a0<em>Born in the U.S.A.\u00a0</em>is certified 7x multi-platinum by the Recording Industry Association of America.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=OLAK5uy_knulz6rBDTjgdDwskLxzD8g7gAdqRY4T0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1992:\u00a0</strong>The Recording Industry Association of America certifies\u00a0<em>Live 1975-85</em> as 12x multi-platinum.</p>\n<p><strong>2008:</strong>\u00a0At Magic Night Two in Oslo, Bruce tour premieres &#8220;If I Should Fall Behind&#8221; (in its only tour appearance) and plays a rare &#8220;From Small Things (Big Things One Day Come).&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-jglWnfIg-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/jglWnfIg?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=PLJTyL9twk3zAhg1pDC7ytrIdtUd3PfUFf\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2009:\u00a0</strong>Bruce brings the Working on a Dream Tour to MCH Arena Herning when the tour makes a brief stop in Denmark.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/_ciF-EgDCDU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2021:\u00a0</strong><em>Springsteen on Broadway\u00a0</em>continues its limited return engagement at the St. James Theater in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>2023:\u00a0</strong>Katy Perry, John Kerry, Chelsea Handler, Orlando Bloom, Judd Apatow, Emma Thompson, Rami Malek, and Tim Robbins are among the star-studded crowd when Bruce and the E Street Band take the stage in Hyde Park for their second of two shows.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/KG7-Z6FyKfw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/la-vOKZsRUU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>One day after the legendary Roxy show, Bruce films some of his most famous live videos in Phoenix. Plus: live performances destined for the Live 1975-85 box set, and more.</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 3186, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "jetpack_post_was_ever_published": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content": false, "footnotes": "", "jetpack_publicize_message": "", "jetpack_publicize_feature_enabled": true, "jetpack_social_post_already_shared": true, "jetpack_social_options": {"image_generator_settings": {"template": "highway", "default_image_id": 0, "font": "", "enabled": false}, "version": 2}}, "categories": [2], "tags": [536, 558, 303, 1236, 535, 508, 829, 610, 961, 1248, 360, 10, 860, 541, 513, 491, 556, 526, 128, 291, 273, 1107, 516], "class_list": ["post-57650", "post", "type-post", "status-publish", "format-standard", "has-post-thumbnail", "hentry", "category-kingdom-of-days", "tag-badlands", "tag-born-in-the-usa-tour", "tag-born-to-run", "tag-bryn-mawr", "tag-candys-room", "tag-darkness-tour", "tag-denmark", "tag-east-rutherford", "tag-herning", "tag-live-1975-85", "tag-magic-tour", "tag-main-point", "tag-norway", "tag-oslo", "tag-phoenix", "tag-prove-it-all-night", "tag-raise-your-hand", "tag-richfield", "tag-river-tour", "tag-rosalita", "tag-springsteen-on-broadway", "tag-